{
  "id": "adv_card_mna_52_01_short",
  "title": "長瀬麻奈 1話 普段と違ーう！ (Short)",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――月のテンペストのライブ数日前",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—A few days before Moon Tempest’s live",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "……もうすぐ月ストのライブ当日か\nまさか、麻奈の誕生日にライブとはなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…It’s almost the day of the Moon Tempest live.\nTo think there’d be a live on Mana’s birthday…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "しかも、あの時のバースデーライブと同じ会場だなんて\nあいつが知ったら、なんて言うかな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And at the same venue as that birthday live back then…\nI wonder what she’d say if she knew…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "もっちろん、私もゲストで出るからね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course‚ I’d be appearing as a guest too!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.0029246409,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01_short/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_mean-09.m4a",
      "text": "全世界がずっと待ってた姉妹共演だもん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The whole world has been waiting for this sisters’ duet.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.7562601169,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "……なんて言いそうだよなぁ\nまぁ、今回はゲストとして、遙子さんが出るんだが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yeah‚ that sounds like something she’d say.\nWell‚ this time‚ Haruko-san will be the guest instead.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.9333344778,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈の誕生日に――\n琴乃のライブに、遙子さんが出るのか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "On Mana’s birthday—\nHaruko-san will be appearing at Kotono’s live…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.9000011445,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――2017年",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—The year 2017",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.759594218,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-00-000-noon",
      "startTime": 41.9262593587
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01_short/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_hey-03.m4a",
      "text": "会場、押さえられたって本当！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is it true you reserved the venue!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.7929260969,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、本当だ\n今年は出来るぞ、長瀬麻奈バースデーライブ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ it’s true.\nThis year we can finally do it—Nagase Mana’s birthday live.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.6666678112,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01_short/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_laughter-08.m4a",
      "text": "やったー！　ありがとう{user}くん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yay! Thank you‚ {user}-kun!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.5338566382,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01_short/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_thank-01.m4a",
      "text": "もう、去年からずーっとずーーっと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ever since last year‚ I’ve been wanting and wanting…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.2338578302,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01_short/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_glad-04.m4a",
      "text": "ずーーーーっと、やりたかったから、嬉しい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "For so——— long! I’m so happy I finally can!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.9338594356,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "本当に出来るんだぁ、バースデーライブ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So it’s really happening… a birthday live…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.3405267378,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}